trans-unit.source: This form should not contain extra fields.
trans-unit.target: Väljade grupp ei tohiks sisalda lisaväljasid.

trans-unit.source: The uploaded file was too large. Please try to upload a smaller file.
trans-unit.target: Üleslaaditud fail oli liiga suur. Palun proovi uuesti väiksema failiga.

trans-unit.source: The CSRF token is invalid. Please try to resubmit the form.
trans-unit.target: CSRF-märgis on vigane. Palun proovi vormi uuesti esitada.
